<view class="page home-page">
  <view class="topbar">失卡招领<text class="en">RUC CAMPUS CARD</text></view>
  <view class="non-official-notice" bindtap="goNotice">
    <b>学生个人公益项目 · 非中国人民大学官方平台</b>
    <text>点击查看运营者信息、使用规则和重要注意事项</text>
  </view>
  <view wx:if="{{cloudError}}" class="cloud-error"><view><b>云端服务暂不可用</b><text>{{cloudError}}</text><text>为避免把假数据当成真实记录，当前不会改用本机数据。</text></view><button loading="{{retrying}}" bindtap="retryCloud">重试</button></view>
  <view class="hero-grid">
    <view class="hero-action lost" bindtap="goLost"><image class="action-icon" src="/assets/icons/search-off-white.png" mode="aspectFit" /><view>我丢卡了</view><text class="en">[ I LOST MY CARD ]</text></view>
    <view class="hero-action found" bindtap="goFound"><image class="action-icon" src="/assets/icons/front-hand.png" mode="aspectFit" /><view>我捡到卡了</view><text class="en">[ I FOUND A CARD ]</text></view>
  </view>
  <view class="neo-card guide">
    <view class="section-heading"><image class="section-icon" src="/assets/icons/info.png" mode="aspectFit" /><view class="section-title">使用说明<text class="en">[ HOW IT WORKS ]</text></view></view><view class="rule" />
    <view class="guide-row"><text class="guide-number number">1</text><text>系统会核对你填写的姓名和学号；</text></view>
    <view class="guide-row"><text class="guide-number number">2</text><text>其他人只能看到隐藏后的姓名和学号；</text></view>
    <view class="guide-row"><text class="guide-number number">3</text><text>姓名学号一致，且有存放照片或卡片已在官方地点后，才会显示存放地点。</text></view>
    <view class="profile-status" bindtap="goProfileEdit">
      <view class="profile-status-copy">
        <block wx:if="{{hasProfile}}"><view>■ 姓名：{{maskedName}}</view><view>■ 学号：{{maskedStudentNumber}}</view><view>■ 状态：{{profileStatus}}</view></block>
        <block wx:else><view class="empty-profile">尚未填写个人信息</view><text>点击填写，查询时自动带入</text></block>
      </view>
      <image class="profile-status-arrow" src="/assets/icons/chevron-right.png" mode="aspectFit" />
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="neo-card visual"><image src="/assets/campus-card-visual.jpg" mode="aspectFill" /><view class="visual-label">中国人民大学 · 校园卡找回</view></view>
</view>
